# Genealogy DNA fossil record
#
# Retired Father agents' DNA snapshots live here, one file per generation
# per lineage, named `father-<tag>-gen<N>.md`. Files are copied in by
# `genealogy/promote/promote-child-agent` during the promotion ceremony
# and are NEVER edited or deleted.
#
# Querying: use Grep against this directory to reconstruct a lineage's
# phylogeny, or pattern `lineage_id: <id>` in the snapshot frontmatter.
